### 4. Implement Email Retries

```typescript
const sendWithRetry = async (message, retries = 3) => {
  for (let i = 0; i < retries; i++) {
    try {
      await mailer.send(message);
      return;
    } catch (error) {
      if (i === retries - 1) throw error;
      await delay(1000 * Math.pow(2, i)); // Exponential backoff
    }
  }
};
```

